{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-385-ellipses-inside-triangles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 385: Elipse unutar kruga","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za bilo koji krug $T$ na ravni, može se dokazati da postoji samo jedna elipsa sa najvećom površinom koja je potpuno unutar $T$.</p>\n<img alt=\"ellipse completely inside a triangle\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/ellipses-inside-triangles.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Za određeni broj $n$, razmotrite krugove $T$ koji imaju:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Verteksi $T$ sa koordinatama celih brojeva koji imaju ceo broj ne veći od $n$, i</li>\n<li>foci<sup>1</sup> za elipsu sa najvećom površinom unutar $T$ su $(\\sqrt{13}, 0)$ i $(-\\sqrt{13}, 0)$.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Neka je $A(n)$ zbir svih kružnih površina na taj način.</p>\n<p>Na primer, ako je $n = 8$, postoji dva takva kruga. Njihovi vrhovi su (-4,-3), (-4,3), (8,0) i (4,3), (4,-3), (-8,0), a površina svakog kruga je 36. Dakle, $A(8) = 36 + 36 = 72$.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da $A(10) = 252$, $A(100) = 34\\,632$ i $A(1000) = 3\\,529\\,008$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $A(1\\,000\\,000\\,000)$.</p>\n<p><sup>1</sup>Fokusi (množina od fokusa) elipse su dve tačke $A$ i $B$, gde je za svaku tačku $P$ na obodu elipse, $AP + PB$ konstantno.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4ee1000cf542c510000","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302049,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-385-ellipses-inside-triangles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function ellipsesInsideTriangles() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nellipsesInsideTriangles();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>ellipsesInsideTriangles()</code> treba return <code>3776957309612154000</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(ellipsesInsideTriangles(), 3776957309612154000);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-385-ellipses-inside-triangles","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-386-maximum-length-of-an-antichain","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-384-rudin-shapiro-sequence","id":"5900f4ee1000cf542c510000","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-385-ellipses-inside-triangles"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}